Definition
=========

1. Structural Design Pattern
2. Reduces the memory usage by sharing data among multiple objects
3. Example -
    a. Design Game
    b. Design Word Processor

When to Use
=========

1. Object Share Data
2. Limited Memory Space
3. Creation of Objects is Expensive


How to Use
=========
1. Remove all uncommon data from object , just keep common object
2. This class can be now made immutable
3. Uncommon data passed as method params
4. Once Flyweight object is created, we can cache the object and reuse it

